MooseX-OmniTrigger

Recursion-proof attribute triggers that fire on any initialize, set, or clear operation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc MooseX::OmniTrigger

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=MooseX-OmniTrigger

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/MooseX-OmniTrigger

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/MooseX-OmniTrigger

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/MooseX-OmniTrigger/

